20messages%20seeking%20comment.%20Her%20flat%20in%20a%20stately%20old%20Budapest%20building%2C%20where%20a%20door%20to%20a%20vestibule%20had%20been%20open%20earlier%20in%20the%20week%2C%20has%20been%20shuttered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussions%20with%20acquaintances%20and%20former%20work%20colleagues%20paint%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20woman%20with%20an%20impressive%20intellect%2C%20but%20a%20peripatetic%20career%20in%20a%20string%20of%20short-term%20jobs%20in%20which%20she%20never%20quite%20settled%20down%2C%20despite%20embellishing%20her%20CV%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20acquaintance%20of%20hers%2C%20who%20like%20others%20who%20knew%20her%20socially%20in%20Budapest%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%2C%20said%20she%20seemed%20like%20someone%20who%20%26quot%3Bcould%20easily%20be%20used%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGood-willed%2C%20not%20a%20business%20type%2C%20more%20like%20someone%20who%20often%20tries%20something%20new%2C%20who%20quickly%20believes%20things%20and%20then%20gets%20enthusiastic%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20person%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Barsony-Arcidiacono%20had%20been%20looking%20for%20income%20as%20she%20wanted%20to%20leave%20another%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'ONE%20OF%20THE%20BIGGEST%20MISTAKES%20OF%20MY%20LIFE'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKilian%20Kleinschmidt%2C%20a%20veteran%20ex-U.N.%20humanitarian%20administrator%20who%20hired%20Barsony-Arcidiacono%20in%202019%20to%20run%20a%20six-month%20Dutch-funded%20programme%20to%20train%20Libyans%20in%20Tunisia%20in%20subjects%20such%20as%20hydroponics%2C%20IT%20and%20business%20development%2C%20described%20her%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbullying%26quot%3B%20manager%2C%20and%20said%20he%20released%20her%20before%20her%20contract%20was%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCristiana.%20That%20was%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20mistakes%20of%20my%20life%2C%20I%20think%2C%26quot%3B%20Kleinschmidt%20told%20Reuters.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20simply%20awful%20on%20a%20personal%20level...%20Then%20at%20some%20point%20I%20said%20enough%20is%20enough.%20I%20should%20probably%20have%20done%20it%20sooner.%20I%20said%20that's%20enough%20and%20I%20sent%20her%20home%20a%20month%20early.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarsony-Arcidiacono%20has%20not%20responded%20to%20Reuters%20calls%20and%20emails%20and%20there%20was%20no%20answer%20when%20Reuters%20visited%20her%20private%20address%20in%20downtown%20Budapest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20her%20Budapest%20home%2C%20a%20steel%20outer%20gate%20encloses%20a%20small%20vestibule%20where%20life%20drawings%20of%20nudes%20sketched%20in%20red%20and%20orange%20pastels%20can%20be%20seen%20taped%20up%20on%20the%20wall.%20An%20inner%20door%20leading%20into%20her%20apartment%20was%20ajar%20when%20Reuters%20first%20visited%20the%20building%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20and%20closed%20when%20the%20reporter%20returned%20on%20Thursday.%20No%20one%20answered%20the%20bell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20living%20in%20the%20building%20for%20the%20past%20two%20years%20said%20Barsony-Arcidiacono%20was%20already%20a%20resident%20when%20she%20moved%20in%2C%20and%20described%20her%20as%20kind%2C%20not%20loud%2C%20but%20communicative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20practiced%20her%20drawing%20as%20part%20of%20a%20Budapest%20art%20club%2C%20though%20she%20hadn't%20attended%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20said%20the%20organiser%20of%20the%20group%2C%20who%20said%20she%20seemed%20like%20more%20of%20a%20businesswoman%20than%20an%20artist%20but%20was%20upbeat%20and%20outgoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20schoolmate%20of%20Barsony-Arcidiacono%20said%20she%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20family%20with%20a%20working%20father%20and%20housewife%20mother%20in%20Santa%20Venerina%2C%20near%20Catania%20in%20eastern%20Sicily%2C%20and%20attended%20high%20school%20nearby.%20He%20described%20her%20as%20a%20quite%20reserved%20youngster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%202000s%20she%20earned%20her%20PhD%20in%20physics%20at%20University%20College%20London%2C%20where%20her%20dissertation%20on%20positrons%20-%20a%20subatomic%20particle%20with%20the%20mass%20of%20an%20electron%20and%20a%20positive%20charge%20-%20remains%20available%20on%20the%20UCL%20website.%20But%20she%20appears%20to%20have%20left%20without%20pursuing%20a%20scientific%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20I%20know%20she%20has%20not%20done%20scientific%20work%20since%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20Akos%20Torok%2C%20a%20retired%20physicists%20who%20was%20one%20of%20her%20professors%20at%20UCL%20and%20published%20papers%20with%20her%20at%20the%20time%2C%20told%20Reuters%20by%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20resume%20she%20used%20to%20get%20the%20job%20working%20for%20Kleinschmidt%20included%20references%20to%20other%20post-graduate%20degrees%2C%20in%20politics%20and%20development%2C%20from%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Economics%20and%20the%20School%20of%20Oriental%20and%20African%20Studies%2C%20which%20Reuters%20was%20not%20able%20to%20verify.%20She%20then%20went%20on%20to%20describe%20a%20string%20of%20jobs%20working%20on%20NGO%20projects%20in%20Europe%2C%20Africa%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20CV%20on%20the%20BAC%20Consulting%20website%2C%20she%20described%20herself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BBoard%20Member%20at%20the%20Earth%20Child%20Institute%26quot%3B%2C%20an%20educational%20and%20environmental%20charity%20in%20New%20York.%20The%20group's%20founder%2C%20Donna%20Goodman%2C%20told%20Reuters%20Barsony-Arcidiacono%20had%20never%20held%20any%20role%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20a%20friend%20of%20a%20friend%20of%20a%20board%20member%2C%20and%20contacted%20us%20about%20a%20job%20opening%26quot%3B%20in%202018%2C%20Goodman%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20she%20was%20never%20invited%20to%20apply.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20CV%20also%20described%20her%20as%20a%20former%20%26quot%3BProject%20Manager%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20International%20Atomic%20Energy%20Agen