22%3A%22Kate%20Middleton%20uses%20this%20parenting%20strategy%20to%20keep%20her%20kids%20disciplined%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726885915000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113539632%2Cimgsize-4383781.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fkate-middleton-uses-this-parenting-strategy-to-keep-her-kids-disciplined%2Farticleshow%2F113539446.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kate%20Middleton%2C%20the%20Princess%20of%20Wales%2C%20employs%20an%20effective%20parenting%20style%20that%20includes%20using%20the%20phrase%20'let's%20take%20a%20break'%20to%20manage%20her%20children's%20behavior.%20Together%20with%20Prince%20William%2C%20they%20prefer%20open%20dialogue%20and%20maintain%20a%20'no%20shouting'%20policy%20at%20home.%20This%20modern%20approach%20ensures%20a%20nurturing%20environment%20for%20their%20children.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Behind%20Making%20Of%20Tirupati%20Laddoos%3A%20How%20Ingredients%20Are%20Procured%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20over%20laddoos%20served%20to%20devotees%20at%20the%20famed%20hill-shrine%20at%20Tirupati%20has%20snowballed%20into%20a%20major%20political%20controversy.%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20has%20claimed%20animal%20fat%20was%20used%20for%20making%20laddoos%20during%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy's%20tenure%2C%20a%20charge%20that%20the%20YSRCP%20leader%20has%20denied.%20The%20centre%20has%20sought%20a%20detailed%20report%20over%20the%20allegations%20while%20the%20Union%20food%20minister%20has%20demanded%20an%20inquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%203%20lakh%20laddoos%20are%20made%20daily%20in%20the%20temple%20kitchen%20at%20Tirupati%2C%20using%20about%201%2C400%20kg%20ghee.%20Vast%20amounts%20of%20cashew%20nuts%2C%20raisins%2C%20cardamoms%2C%20gram%20flour%2C%20and%20sugar%20are%20also%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tirumala%20Tirupati%20Devasthanams%20(TTD)%2C%20which%20manages%20the%20Sri%20Venkateswara%20Swami%20temple%20in%20Tirupati%2C%20buys%20the%20ingredients%20through%20e-auction%2C%20spending%20about%20Rs%20500%20crore%20on%20the%20procurement.%20The%20tendering%20process%20had%20shifted%20to%20online%20in%202022%20to%20reduce%20human%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ghee%20tankers%20come%20with%20certification%20by%20the%20National%20Accreditation%20Board%20for%20Testing%20and%20Calibration%20Laboratories%20(NABL)%2C%20which%20ensures%20food%20testing%20has%20been%20done%20reliably.%20The%20consignment%20is%20stocked%20in%20godowns%20spread%20over%20two%20acres%20near%20Alipiri%20in%20Tirupati%20-%20for%20use%20in%20prasada%20as%20well%20as%20for%20its%20free%20food%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20procurement%20includes%20over%206%2C100%20tonne%20ghee%2C%2014%20tonnes%20sugar%2C%209%2C200%20tonnes%20of%20Bengal%20gram%2C%204%2C680%20tonnes%20sona%20masoori%20dal%2C%20and%20other%20ingredients%20that%20include%20raisins%2C%20cashews%2C%20cardamom%20and%20sunflower%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20those%20agencies%20registered%20with%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Technological%20Services%20are%20allowed%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20e-auction.%20The%20contracts%20are%20awarded%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20various%20technical%20parameters%20and%20financial%20factors.%20AGMARK%20certification%20and%20FSSAI%20licences%20are%20a%20must%20for%20such%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnline%20reverse%20tendering%20is%20also%20followed%20for%20orders%20above%20Rs%201%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consignment%20that%20has%20come%20under%20spotlight%20included%2010%20tankers%20of%20ghee%20from%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu-based%20AR%20Dairy%20Food%20Pvt%20Ltd.%20Four%20of%20their%20tankers%20were%20stopped%20over%20suspected%20adulteration.%20The%20samples%20were%20sent%20for%20testing%20and%20the%20consignment%20was%20kept%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAR%20Dairy%20has%20said%20its%20consignments%20have%20cleared%20multiple%20lab%20tests%20and%20that%20they%20have%20documents%20to%20prove%20all%20test%20reports%20had%20cleared%20the%20ghee%20which%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20temple.%20The%20dairy%20said%20it%20supplied%20just%200.01%20per%20cent%20ghee%20to%20Tirumala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnimal%20Fat%20In%20Laddoos%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Naidu%20government%20this%20week%20flagged%20a%20July%2017%20report%20that%20said%20ghee%20samples%20from%20Tirupati%20contained%20fish%20oil%2C%20beef%20tallow%2C%20and%20lard%2C%20a%20form%20of%20pig%20fat.%20%26quot%3BEven%20Tirupati%20laddoo%20was%20made%20with%20substandard%20ingredients.%20They%20used%20animal%20fat%20instead%20of%20ghee%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20told%20a%20legislature%20meeting%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%2C%20who%20lost%20the%20state%20elections%20this%20year%2C%20hit%20back%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20report%26quot%3B%20and%20accused%20Mr%20Naidu%20of%20%26quot%3Busing%20faith%20for%20politics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TTD%20has%20also%20backed%20Mr%20Naidu's%20claims.%20TTD%20Executive%20Officer%20J%20Shyamala%20Rao%20said%20that%20suppliers%20took%20advantage%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20an%20in-house%20testing%20facility%20and%20they%20are%20in%20the%20process%20of%20blacklisting%20the%20concerned%20contractor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20laddoo%20row%20has%20also%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20with%20a%20petition%20being%20filed%20alleging%20violation%20of%20Article%2025%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20guarantees%20the%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20religion%2C%20including%20the%20right%20to%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726885560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Ftg4898a8_tirupati-temple_625x300_20_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.co