%247%20million%20bounty%20on%20Aqil%20for%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%201983%20bombings%20that%20killed%20hundreds%20of%20Americans%20in%20Lebanon.%20Aqil%20was%20also%20implicated%20in%20the%20kidnapping%20of%20American%20and%20European%20hostages%20in%20the%201980s.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20airstrike%2C%20which%20struck%20Hezbollah's%20stronghold%20in%20southern%20Beirut%2C%20left%20significant%20damage%2C%20including%20a%20massive%20crater%20and%20a%20destroyed%20high-rise%20building.%20Rescue%20workers%20continued%20to%20search%20the%20rubble%20for%20survivors.%20%C2%A0In%20response%20to%20the%20airstrike%2C%20Hezbollah%20fired%20dozens%20of%20rockets%20at%20Israeli%20military%20positions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAqil's%20death%20marks%20a%20serious%20blow%20to%20Hezbollah's%20leadership%2C%20especially%20as%20it%20comes%20just%20weeks%20after%20the%20death%20of%20Fuad%20Shukr%2C%20another%20senior%20Hezbollah%20commander%2C%20in%20a%20similar%20Israeli%20airstrike.%20Both%20men%20were%20top%20figures%20within%20Hezbollah's%20military%20operations%20and%20played%20key%20roles%20in%20planning%20attacks%20against%20Israel.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20strike%20follows%20two%20days%20of%20explosions%20earlier%20in%20the%20week%2C%20which%20targeted%20Hezbollah's%20communication%20devices%20and%20killed%2037%20of%20its%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIsraeli%20military%20officials%20said%20that%20Aqil%20was%20killed%20while%20meeting%20with%20other%20commanders%20to%20plan%20further%20attacks%20against%20Israel%2C%20including%20a%20potential%20invasion%20of%20northern%20Israeli%20territories.%20The%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20described%20the%20meeting%20as%20part%20of%20Hezbollah's%20%26quot%3BConquer%20the%20Galilee%26quot%3B%20plan%2C%20an%20operation%20aimed%20at%20infiltrating%20Israeli%20communities.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20and%20regional%20actors%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20growing%20escalation.%20UN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres'%20spokesman%2C%20Stephane%20Dujarric%2C%20called%20for%20restraint%20from%20all%20sides.%20The%20strike%20has%20also%20drawn%20strong%20condemnation%20from%20Iran%2C%20which%20supports%20Hezbollah%2C%20accusing%20Israel%20of%20broadening%20the%20war's%20geography.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIran's%20foreign%20ministry%20denounced%20the%20attack%20as%20a%20violation%20of%20international%20law%2C%20while%20Hezbollah%20vowed%20retribution.%20Israel%2C%20however%2C%20defended%20the%20operation%20as%20necessary%20for%20its%20national%20security.%20Admiral%20Daniel%20Hagari%2C%20an%20Israeli%20military%20spokesman%2C%20stressed%20that%20Israel%20did%20not%20seek%20a%20broader%20conflict%20but%20was%20determined%20to%20neutralise%20threats%20to%20its%20citizens.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHezbollah%20and%20Israeli%20forces%20have%20exchanged%20fire%20almost%20daily%20along%20the%20Israel-Lebanon%20border%20since%20the%20Gaza%20war%20began%20in%20October.%20The%20war%2C%20sparked%20by%20Hamas'%20deadly%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20has%20drawn%20Hezbollah%20into%20the%20conflict.%20Hezbollah%20has%20launched%20rocket%20attacks%20into%20northern%20Israel%2C%20which%20have%20intensified%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELebanon's%20Health%20Ministry%20reported%20that%20the%20strike%20killed%2014%20people%20and%20wounded%2066%20others%2C%20and%20they%20expect%20the%20death%20count%20to%20rise.%20Local%20residents%20have%20described%20the%20bombardment%20as%20some%20of%20the%20heaviest%20in%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726882560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F7rj5usn_israel-hezbollah-_625x300_21_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hezbollah-lebanon-hezbollah-commander-carrying-7-million-bounty-killed-in-beirut-strike-6614255%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel%20announced%20Friday%20that%20it%20killed%20Ibrahim