%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726880408000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113539033%2Cimgsize-1740921.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fimphal%2Fmanipur-flags-intel-on-influx-of-900-tribal-rebels-from-myanmar%2Farticleshow%2F113539004.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Manipur%20CM%20Biren%20Singh's%20office%20has%20forwarded%20to%20police%20a%20purported%20intelligence%20alert%20about%20an%20influx%20of%20900-odd%20tribal%20militants%20from%20Myanmar%20as%20part%20of%20a%20mission%20to%20launch%20attacks%20on%20villages%20in%20Imphal%20valley%20around%20Sept%2028.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22PRABIN%20KALITA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fimphal%2Fmanipur-flags-intel-on-influx-of-900-tribal-rebels-from-myanmar%2Farticleshow%2F113539004.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suspected%20Trump%20Assassination%20Plotter%20Has%20Criminal%20History%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20erratic%20life%20of%20a%20struggling%20roofing%20contractor%20suspected%20of%20trying%20to%20shoot%20Donald%20Trump%20swerved%20from%20bounced%20checks%20to%20a%20weapon%20felony%20conviction%20and%20a%20quixotic%20plan%20to%20help%20Ukraine%20fight%20Russia's%20invasion%2C%20before%20culminating%20in%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20foiled%20assassination%20plot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERyan%20Routh%2C%2058%2C%20was%20charged%20with%20two%20gun-related%20crimes%20in%20a%20federal%20court%20in%20Florida%20on%20Monday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20he%20was%20spotted%20with%20a%20rifle%20hiding%20in%20shrubbery%20on%20the%20property%20line%20of%20Trump's%20golf%20course.%20More%20charges%20are%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20have%20not%20cited%20any%20possible%20motives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERouth%20mocked%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20on%20social%20media%20and%20suggested%20in%20a%202023%20self-published%20book%20that%20he%20voted%20for%20Trump%20in%202016.%20But%20he%20then%20wrote%20that%20backing%20Trump%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrible%20mistake%26quot%3B%20and%20at%20various%20points%20described%20the%20former%20president%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfool%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20%26quot%3Bbuffoon%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20an%20%26quot%3Bidiot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20Iran%2C%20Routh%20wrote%20that%20%26quot%3Byou%20are%20free%20to%20assassinate%20Trump%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20former%20president's%20decision%20to%20withdraw%20the%20United%20States%20from%20the%20Iran%20nuclear%20deal%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20291-page%20book%20%26quot%3BUkraine's%20Unwinnable%20War%2C%26quot%3B%20Routh%20argued%20that%20democracy%20needed%20defending%20around%20the%20world%20and%20the%20United%20States%20had%20its%20own%20%26quot%3Bcatastrophe%26quot%3B%20on%20Jan%206%2C%202021%2C%20%26quot%3Bperpetrated%20by%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20undemocratic%20posse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECourt%20records%20showed%20Routh%20has%20a%20long%20history%20of%20breaking%20traffic%20laws%2C%20not%20paying%20his%20taxes%20on%20time%20and%20writing%20bad%20checks.%20But%20it%20was%20in%202002%20that%20he%20lost%20his%20right%20to%20own%20a%20gun%20when%20he%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20a%20felony%20in%20North%20Carolina%20for%20possessing%20an%20illegal%20explosive%20device%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonths%20after%20his%20arrest%20in%20that%20case%20while%20released%20on%20a%20bond%2C%20Routh%20fled%20from%20a%20traffic%20stop%20by%20a%20police%20officer%20near%20his%20home%20in%20Greensboro%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20and%20barricaded%20himself%20inside%20his%20roofing%20business%20for%20several%20hours%20before%20police%20were%20able%20to%20arrest%20him%20for%20having%20a%20concealed%20handgun%20without%20a%20permit%2C%20according%20to%20court%20records%20and%20a%202002%20news%20article%20by%20the%20Greensboro%20News%20%26amp%3B%20Record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20Routh%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20possession%20of%20what%20court%20records%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbinary%20explosive%20with%20a%2010-inch%20detonation%20cord%20and%20a%20blasting%20cap%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20defined%20in%20North%20Carolina%20law%20as%20a%20weapon%20of%20mass%20destruction%20and%20is%20a%20felony%20punishable%20by%20up%20to%2059%20months%20in%20prison%2C%20according%20to%20the%20county%20district%20attorney's%20office%20and%20the%20Guilford%20County%20Superior%20Court%20clerk's%20office.%20He%20was%20sentenced%20to%20probation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEight%20years%20later%2C%20he%20again%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20felonies%20after%20he%20was%20charged%20with%20possession%20of%20stolen%20goods%3A%20a%20blowtorch%2C%20a%20pull-cart%20and%20a%20power%20cord%2C%20according%20to%20the%20district%20attorney's%20office.%20As%20the%20owner%20of%20several%20roofing%20companies%2C%20he%20has%20been%20repeatedly%20sued%20by%20people%20accusing%20him%20of%20not%20paying%20his%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20it%20received%20a%20tip%20in%202019%20that%20Routh%20was%20a%20felon%20in%20possession%20of%20a%20firearm%20-%20prohibited%20by%20federal%20law%20-%20but%20that%20the%20person%20who%20made%20that%20tip%20would%20later%20not%20confirm%20the%20information%20during%20an%20interview%20with%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20relayed%20the%20tip%20to%20local%20authorities%20in%20Hawaii%2C%20where%20Routh%20moved%20in%202018%20after%20decades%20in%20North%20Carolina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPOSTS%20ON%20UKRAINE%2C%20DEMOCRACY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReuters%20found%20profiles%20on%20X%2C%20Facebook%20and%20LinkedIn%20for%20a%20Ryan%20Routh%2C%20and%20public%20access%20to%20the%20Facebook%20and%20X%20profiles%20was%20removed%20hours%20after%20the%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20accounts%20bearing%20Routh's%20name%20showed%20he%20supported%20Ukraine%20in%20its%20war%20against%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2021%2C%20Routh%20directed%20an%20X%20message%20to%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20writing%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20buy%20a%20rocket%20from%20you.%20I%20wish%20to%20load%20it%20with%20a%20warhead%20for%20Putins%20Black%20sea%20mansion%20bunker%20to%20end%20him.%20Can%20you%20give%20me%20a%20price%20please.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%20reported%20it%20had%20interviewed%20Routh%20in%202023%20for%20an%20article%20about%20Americans%20who%20were%20volunteering%20to%20help%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20effort.%20Routh%20told%20the%20Times%20he%20traveled%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20spent%20several%20months%20there%20in%202022%20and%20was%20trying%20to%20recruit%20Afghan%20soldiers%20who%20fled%20the%20Taliban%20to%20fight%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20current%20and%20another%20former%20U.S.%20volunteer%20serving%20with%20the%20foreign%20legion%20of%20Ukraine's%20army%20said%20they%20recalled%20Routh%20and%20believed%20that%20he%20spent%20time%20in%20the%20western%20Ukrainian%20city%20of%20Ivano-Frankivsk.%20Both%20of%20them%20said%20he%20exhibited%20odd%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERouth%20was%20blocked%20from%20the%20%26quot%3BVolunteers%20for%20Ukraine%26quot%3B%20chat%20group%20on%20Signal%20last%20year%20and%20blacklisted%2C%20after%20appearing%20%26quot%3Bdelusional%26quot%3B%20with%20promises%20to%20bring%20foreign%20volunteer%20recruits%20to%20the%20country%20despite%20having%20no%20military%20background%2C%20said%20a%20former%20U.S.%20volunteer%20with%20the%20legion%2C%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20on%20leave%20in%20the%20west%20from%20battle%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20he%20and%20fellow%20volunteers%20tried%20their%20best%20to%20avoid%20Routh%20and%20others%20who%20made%20such%20grand%20promises%2C%20the%20volunteer%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Legion%2C%20where%20many%20foreign%20fighters%20in%20Ukraine%20s