kota%20(SSN%20784)%20submarine%20is%20seen%20during%20bravo%20sea%20trials%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5b69b21364dce8fb438b4631%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221462%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Navy%20attributed%20shipbuilding%20delays%20across%20its%20top%20programs%20to%20COVID-19's%20impact%20on%20the%20workforce%20and%20supply%20chain.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FU.S.%20Navy%2FHandout%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20remarks%2C%20Calvert%20noted%20the%20Navy%20is%20struggling%20to%20construct%20just%201.3%20of%20the%20vessels%20a%20year%20when%20its%C2%A0requirement%20is%20two%2C%20and%20the%20cost%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20%2417%20billion%20more%20than%20budgeted%20through%202030.%20It's%20unclear%20what%20exactly%20is%20included%20in%20that%20figure%20and%20whether%20it%20could%20be%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20clear%20that%20the%20Navy%20and%20shipbuilders%20have%20known%20about%20this%20shortfall%20for%20at%20least%2018%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Calvert%20added%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3Bwhen%20Congress%20was%20notified%20just%20two%20weeks%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Congressional%20hearing%20was%20held%20as%20Navy%20Secretary%20Carlos%20Del%20Toro%20attempted%20to%20advocate%20for%20the%20Shipyard%20Accountability%20and%20Workforce%20Support%20proposal%2C%20which%20was%20shot%20down%20by%20the%20White%20House.%20The%20proposal%20sought%20to%20reallocate%20money%20set%20aside%20for%20future%20Virginia-%20and%20Columbia-class%20submarines%20to%20cover%20shipyards'%20current%20inflation-related%20costs%20and%20worker%20pay%20issues%2C%20both%20of%20which%20the%20Navy%20and%20its%20industry%20partners%20have%20said%20are%20causing%20schedule%20delays%20and%20funding%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20regard%20to%20the%20SAWS%20proposal%2C%20HII%20CEO%20and%20President%20Christopher%20Kastner%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Freporterjoe%2Fstatus%2F1836741039228432573%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20Politico%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20credit%20Secretary%20Del%20Toro%2C%20the%20Navy%2C%20and%20DOD%20with%20a%20solution%20that%20is%20kind%20of%20genius%3A%20addresses%20the%20wage%20gap%20and%20invests%20in%20the%20industrial%20base%20without%20the%20need%20for%20funding%20above%20the%20Navy's%20planned%20budget.%20It%20gets%20at%20the%20underlying%20current%20challenges%20in%20shipbuilding%20so%20we%20can%20get%20these%20ships%20built%20and%20delivered%20on%20schedule%20to%20support%20the%20Navy%20and%20AUKUS.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20after%20the%20Congressional%20hearing%2C%20the%20Navy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.navy.mil%2FPress-Office%2FPress-Releases%2Fdisplay-pressreleases%2FArticle%2F3911791%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20Del%20Toro%C2%A0%26quot%3Brecognized%20the%20importance%20of%20submarine%20acquisitions%20amidst%20the%20challenges%20of%20fiscal%20constraints.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20added%20that%20Del%20Toro%20%26quot%3Bhas%20been%20advocating%20for%20improvements%20to%20the%20maritime%20industrial%20base%2C%20and%20to%20increase%20funding%20to%20ensure%20the%20Navy%20meets%20its%20acquisition%20objectives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20alleviate%20its%20cost%20and%20manufacturing%20problems%2C%20the%20Navy%20added%20that%20it%20had%20created%20an%20independent%20cost%20agency%20to%20increase%C2%A0accuracy%20on%20program%20costs%20and%20was%20working%20to%20streamline%20ship%20design%20processes%20and%20improve%20shipyard%20facilities%20as%20it%20aims%20to%20grow%20its%20fleet%20to%20counter%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22922%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chart%20from%20the%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Navy's%2045-day%20Shipbuilding%20Review.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660d8ec93f923f7dab042c13%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Navy's%20bigg