ption%3EAMC%20Theatres%20is%20one%20of%20the%20chains%20that%20will%20be%20modernizing%20its%20facilities.%20For%20some%20locations%2C%20that%20includes%20pickleball%20courts.%3Cp%3EAaronP%2FBauer-Griffin%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMovie%20theatre%20chains%20are%20adding%20pickleball%20courts%20and%20ziplines%20to%20their%20properties.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20top%20US%20chains%20are%20investing%20%242.2%20billion%20to%20modernize%20their%20facilities%20and%20add%20new%20activities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETheaters%20will%20also%20upgrade%20seats%2C%20projection%20technology%2C%20sound%20quality%2C%20and%20snacks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20struggling%20movie%20theater%20industry%20has%20a%20buzzy%20new%20idea%20for%20how%20to%20solve%20its%20financial%20woes%3A%20pickleball.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20ziplining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Association%20of%20Theater%20Owners%2C%20a%20trade%20organization%20that%20represents%20the%20eight%20largest%20theater%20chains%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Canada%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheatreowners.org%2F2024%2F09%2F19%2Ftheatre-owners-to-invest-more-than-2-2-billion-in-the-cinematic-experience%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%20in%20a%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20Thursday%20that%20it%20will%20invest%20more%20than%20%242.2%20billion%20over%20the%20next%20three%20years%20to%20modernize%20its%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20that%20money%20will%20go%20toward%20renovations%20that%20many%20movie%20theaters%20across%20the%20country%20desperately%20need%2C%20such%20as%20more%20comfortable%20seats%2C%20higher-quality%20projection%20technology%20and%20sound%20systems%2C%20and%20better%20snacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20association%20said%20other%20crucial%20updates%20will%20include%20installing%20better%20air%20conditioning%2C%20lighting%2C%20carpeting%2C%20and%20signage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20not%20all.%20The%20group%20said%2