22A%20pile%20of%20white%20blocks%20near%20a%20hill%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ec887fce3009a0fac7d7ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221382%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20Bischoff%20started%20examining%20blocks%20from%20the%20SPHS%20site%2C%20he%20realized%20the%20were%20full%20of%20fossils.%3Cp%3EEnvicom%20Corporation%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Bischoff%20was%20visiting%20the%20construction%20site%20when%20he%20realized%20limestone%20blocks%20taken%20from%20below%20the%201936%20courtyard%20contained%20the%20remains%20of%20animals%20far%20more%20complex%20than%20simple%20mollusks%3A%20they%20were%20fish%20and%20mammal%20bones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20hosing%20off%20the%20mud-caked%20blocks%2C%20Bischoff%20and%20the%20construction%20workers%20discovered%20an%20astonishing%20amount%20of%20fossils.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20volume%20of%20fish%20bones%20was%20remarkable%2C%20but%20coming%20across%20baleen%20whale%20vertebra%20was%20the%20most%20amazing%2C%26quot%3B%20Bischoff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20finding%20kicked%20off%20a%20huge%20salvage%20project%20to%20record%20and%20date%20the%20fossils%2C%20which%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20roughly%208.7%20million%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELos%20Angeles%20used%20to%20be%20under%20water.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20large%20containing%20dolphin%20and%20fish%20fossils%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66edae16ce3009a0fac821e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20large%20rock%20contains%20countless%20fossils%2C%20including%20dolphin%20vertebrae%20and%20fish%20bones.%3Cp%3EAustin%20Hendy%2FCourtesy%20of%20the%20Natural%20History%20Museums%20of%20Los%20Angeles%20County%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20blocks%20contain%20everything%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus