-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erein%20in%20inflation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20skewing%20hawkish%20among%20the%20Fed's%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20keep%20in%20mind%20the%20historical%20lessons%20and%20risks%20associated%20with%20prematurely%20declaring%20victory%20in%20the%20fight%20against%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20Bowman%20said%20in%20a%20speech%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-reserve-dissent-michelle-bowman-inflation-big-rate-cut-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726859540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6606da6b16bde8d4ead3a243%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-reserve-dissent-michelle-bowman-inflation-big-rate-cut-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Michelle%20Bowman%20said%20such%20a%20big%20initial%20rate%20cut%20could%20complicate%20the%20Fed's%20mission%20of%20getting%20inflation%20back%20to%20its%202%25%20target.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kcloonan%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Cloonan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-reserve-dissent-michelle-bowman-inflation-big-rate-cut-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Aamir%20bluntly%20rejected%20the%20idea%20of%20Jaane%20Tu%20sequel'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726859227000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113534677%2Cimgsize-19906.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fabbas-tyrewala-recalls-how-aamir-khan-bluntly-rejected-the-idea-of-jaane-tu-ya-jaane-na-sequel-the-stupidest-thing%2Farticleshow%2F113534662.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofi