%20and%20corruption%20charges%20linked%20to%20the%20liquor%20policy%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20while%20ordering%20his%20bail%20in%20the%20former%20case%20(after%20granting%20relief%20in%20the%20latter%20in%20July)%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20his%20%26quot%3Bprolonged%20incarceration%20amounts%20to%20unjust%20deprivation%20of%20liberty%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bail%20conditions%20included%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20being%20barred%20from%20signing%20government%20orders%20or%20files%20without%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%2C%20with%20whom%20the%20AAP%20has%20had%20several%20aggressive%20run-ins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%2C%20Congress%20On%20AAP's%20Move%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20announced%20her%20as%20his%20replacement%2C%20Atishi%20said%2C%20This%20is%20an%20emotional%20moment%20for%20the%20party%20and%20people%20of%20Delhi.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20people%20are%20resolved%20to%20make%20Kejriwal%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20again.%20And%2C%20till%20the%20election%20is%20held%20and%20we%20stake%20claim%20to%20the%20new%20government%2C%20I%20will%20look%20after%20Delhi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20hit%20back%2C%20questioning%20if%20this%20decision%20was%20due%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Brift%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20that%20its%20leader%20cannot%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20didn't%20resign%20when%20in%20jail%2C%20but%20are%20now%20announcing%20that%20you%20will%20resign%20in%2048%20hours%3F%20People%20want%20to%20know%20the%20mystery%20behind%20these%2048%20hours.%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20discharge%20duties%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20why%20do%20you%20need%2048%20hours%3F%26quot%3B%20BJP%20MP%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20which%20fought%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20Delhi%20in%20alliance%20with%20AAP%2C%20described%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20resignation%20announcement%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20stunt%26quot%3B.%20Delhi%20Congress%20chief%20Devender%20Yadav%20said%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20resigned%20because%20he%20has%20no%20powers%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20is%20bound%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20conditions.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20political%20stunt%20and%20nothing%20else.%20This%20will%20have%20no%20impact%20on%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%20People%20want%20change%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726857480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Ff39bb6hg_aatishi_650x400_19_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fatishi-to-take-oath-tomorrow-will-be-delhis-youngest-chief-minister-6612218%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%20Atishi%20will%20take%20oath%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Delhi%20today%20at%204%3A30%20pm.%20The%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20will%20take%20place%20at%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20-%20the%20Lt%20Governor's%20residence%20-%20and%20five%20AAP%20MLAs%20will%20take%20oath%20along%20with%20Atishi%20as%20ministers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Abbas%20Tyrewala%20confirms%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20'Pathaan%202'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726857437000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113533774%2Cimgsize-33038.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fabbas-tyrewala-confirms-shah-rukh-khans-pathaan-2-says-script-almost-ready-%2Farticleshow%2F113533788.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113533788.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAbbas%20Tyrewala%20has%20revealed%20that%20'Pathaan%202'%20is%20scheduled%2C%20with%20the%20s