mple%2C%20Says%20Amul%20Amid%20Laddoo%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20a%20row%20over%20the%20use%20of%20animal%20fat%20in%20prasada%20given%20at%20Tirumala%20temple%20in%20Andhra's%20Tirupati%20district%2C%20Amul%20issued%20a%20clarification%20on%20Friday%2C%20stating%20that%20it%20had%20never%20supplied%20ghee%20to%20Tirumala%20Tirupati%20Devasthanam%20(TTD).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20posts%20on%20various%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20Amul.coop%20posted%20a%20statement%20on%20X%2C%20stating%20that%20Amul%20Ghee%20was%20never%20supplied%20to%20the%20TTD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20in%20reference%20to%20some%20social%20media%20posts%20mentioning%20that%20Amul%20Ghee%20was%20being%20supplied%20to%20Tirumala%20Tirupati%20Devasthanam%20(TTD).%20We%20wish%20to%20inform%20that%20we%20have%20never%20supplied%20Amul%20Ghee%20to%20TTD%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIssued%20in%20Public%20Interest%20by%20Amul%20pic.twitter.com%2Fj7uobwDtJI%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Amul.coop%20(%40Amul_Coop)%20September%2020%2C%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20wish%20to%20clarify%20Amul%20Ghee%20is%20made%20from%20milk%20at%20our%20state-of-the-art%20production%20facilities%2C%20which%20are%20ISO%20certified.%20Amul%20Ghee%20is%20made%20from%20high-quality%20pure%20milk%20fat.%20The%20milk%20received%20at%20our%20dairies%20passes%20through%20stringent%20quality%20checks%2C%20including%20adulteration%20detection%20as%20specified%20by%20FSSAI%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20came%20two%20days%20after%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20claimed%20that%20substandard%20ingredients%2C%20including%20animal%20fat%2C%20were%20used%20in%20the%20preparation%20of%20Tirupati%20laddus%2C%20a%20sweet%20offered%20at%20the%20Sri%20Venkateswara%20temple%20in%20Tirupati%2C%20during%20the%20previous%20Yuvajana%20Sramika%20Rythu%20Congress%20Party%20(YSRCP)%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20Tirupati%20laddu%20issue%2C%20former%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20YS%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20stated%20that%20the%20TDP%20is%20%26quot%3Bpoliticising%20religious%20matters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tender%20process%20occurs%20every%20six%20months%2C%20and%20the%20qualification%20criteria%20have%20not%20changed%20for%20decades.%20Suppliers%20must%20provide%20an%20NABL%20certificate%20and%20a%20product%20quality%20certificate.%20The%20TTD%20collects%20samples%20of%20the%20ghee%2C%20and%20only%20products%20that%20pass%20certification%20are%20used.%20The%20TDP%20is%20politicising%20religious%20matters.%20In%20our%20regime%2C%20we%20have%20rejected%20products%2018%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20Reddy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Health%20Minister%20JP%20Nadda%20on%20Friday%20spoke%20to%20CM%20Naidu%20and%20sought%20a%20full%20report%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Centre%20would%20examine%20the%20matter%20and%20take%20suitable%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20briefing%20on%20the%20Modi%20government's%20100-day%20achievements%2C%20Nadda%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20adulteration%20in%20Tirupati%20prasadam%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20spoken%20to%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20CM%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20after%20receiving%20information%20about%20this%20and%20took%20details%20from%20him.%20I%20have%20asked%20him%20to%20share%20the%20available%20report%20so%20that%20I%20can%20examine%20it.%20I%20will%20also%20speak%20to%20the%20state%20regulators%20and%20investigate%20this.%20Suitable%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20as%20per%20the%20food%20safety%20standards.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20I%20have%20asked%20for%20the%20report%20and%20we%20will%20examine%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYSRCP%20chief%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20on%20Friday%20said%20that%20he%20will%20write%20a%20letter%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20and%20claimed%20that%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20has%20twisted%20the%20facts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20I%20myself%20am%20writing%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20I%20am%20also%20writing%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India.%20I%20am%20explaining%20to%20them%20as%20to%20how%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20twisted%20the%20facts%20and%20why%20action%20should%20be%20taken%20against%20him%20for%20having%20done%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20YSRCP%20chief%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDP%20MP%20Sribharat%20Mathukumilli%20said%20that%20the%20reports%20categorically%20said%20that%20a%20particular%20fat%20based%20on%20its%20S%20value%20is%20not%20within%20the%20stipulated%20range%20and%20is%20not%20milk%20fat%2C%20it%20is%20not%20ghee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20received%20the%20lab%20reports%20of%20ghee%20used%20in%20making%20Tirupati%20Laddus.%20Both%20reports%20categorically%20said%20that%20a%20particular%20fat%20based%20on%20its%20S%20value%20is%20not%20within%20the%20stipulated%20range%20and%20is%20not%20milk%20fat%2C%20it%20is%20not%20ghee.%20It%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20vegetable%20oils%20and%2C%20shockingly%2C%20beef%20fat%20and%20pig%20fat.%20This%20has%20shaken%20devotees%20and%20all%20followers%20of%20Hinduism%20across%20the%20country.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20such%20kind%20of%20governance%20was%20plaguing%20not%20just%20the%20state%20but%20also%20the%20holy%20site%20of%20Tirumala%20Tirupati%20Devasthanam...%20The%20hurt%20it%20has%20caused%20cannot%20be%20resolved%20so%20easily.%20People%20across%20the%20country%20are%20grieving...%20A%20similar%20case%20has%20come%20forward%20in%20the%20Simhachalam%20Temple%20also%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20TDP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E