20President%2C%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%2C%20is%20credited%20for%20bringing%20stability%20to%20the%20economy%2C%20but%20you%20are%20saying%20he%20is%20part%20of%20the%20problem%20and%20not%20the%20solution%20-%20that%20is%20a%20serious%20charge.%20Can%20you%20please%20elaborate%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EA)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20one%20takes%20out%20their%20laurels%20and%20gets%20on%20to%20the%20streets%20and%20talks%20to%20the%20poor%2C%20the%20downtrodden%2C%20the%20self-employed%2C%20the%20labour%20force%2C%20the%20entrepreneurs%2C%20the%20rural%20and%20urban%20estate%20sectors%3B%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20major%20sections%20of%20society%2C%20other%20than%20those%20who%20are%20super%20rich%2C%20people%20who%20have%20been%20impacted%20detrimentally%2C%20and%20if%20I%20may%20provide%20you%20with%20some%20statistics...%20stats%20which%20were%20ascertained%20by%20the%20government%20statistical%20department%20has%20Illustrated%20that%20more%20than%20260%2C000%20micro%2C%20small%20and%20medium%20sized%20enterprises%20have%20closed.%20Millions%20have%20become%20unemployed%2C%20millions%20more%20have%20become%20poor%2C%20and%20the%20government%20does%20not%20have%20a%20strategy%20to%20deal%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20micro%2C%20small%2C%20and%20medium%20sized%20enterprises%20contribute%20to%2050%25%20of%20GDP%2C%20employs%20over%204%20million%2C%20so%20people%20are%20suffering%20from%20the%20policies%20of%20a%20government%20that%20has%20basically%20suffocated%20the%20people.%20So%2C%20if%20you%20achieving%20stability%20at%20great%20human%20cost...%20at%20a%20cost%20where%20people%20are%20suffering%2C%C2%A0%20then%20I%20don't%20think%20that's%20the%20right%20way%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ)%20So%2C%20in%20comparison%2C%20what%20is%20your%20action%20plan%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EA)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Where%20we%20defer%2C%20is%20that%20we%20will%20grow%20ourselves%20out%20of%20the%20problem.%20We%20have%20to%