0the%20economy%20further%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EA)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20will%20eradicate%20the%20crony-capitalist%20structure%20that%20is%20existing%20at%20present.%20We%20will%20ensure%20that%20growth%20is%20the%20major%20phenomenon%20in%20our%20economic%20program.%20This%20government%20doesn't%20understand%20growth.%20They%20are%20contracting%20growth.%20To%20show%20everybody%20that%20the%20economy%20is%20stable%2C%20you're%20making%20everything%20smaller%20-%20That%20is%20not%20the%20way%20to%20go.%20We%20have%20to%20grow%20ourselves%20out%20of%20the%20problem.%20So%2C%20stability%20with%20malnutrition%2C%20stability%20with%20huge%20unemployment%2C%20stability%20with%20growth%20contraction%2C%20stability%20while%20losing%20livelihoods%2C%20stability%20while%20having%20lower%20standards%20of%20living...%20I'm%20sorry%2C%20I%20don't%20agree%20with%20that.%20The%20difference%20between%20the%20government%20and%20us%20is%20that%20we%20don't%20just%20focus%20on%20macroeconomics%2C%20we%20also%20look%20at%20the%20microeconomics.%20So%2C%20we%20are%20taking%20an%20overarching%20integrated%20approach%2C%20whereas%20this%20government%20is%20only%20keen%20on%20showing%20to%20the%20whole%20world%20and%20to%20a%20particular%20class%20in%20our%20country%20that%20everything%20is%20stable%20and%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ)%20India%20has%20strategic%20interests%20in%20the%20region.%20India%20had%20and%20still%20has%20very%20close%20ties%20with%20Sri%20Lanka.%20How%20do%20you%20view%20the%20India-Sri%20Lanka%20relationship%20from%20here%20on%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EA)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20you%20talk%20of%20recovery%2C%20I%20must%20say%20in%20these%20very%20difficult%20and%20dire%20times%2C%20India%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20countries%20that%20has%20been%20very%20generous%2C%20and%20very%20supportive...%20and%20I%20would%20like%20to%20extend%20a%20very%20big%20thank%20you%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20PM%20Modi's%20g