20reporters%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intelligence%20report%20was%20sent%20to%20all%20Senior%20Superintendents%20of%20Police%20in%20the%20districts%20along%20the%20India-Myanmar%20border%20in%20southern%20Manipur%2C%20top%20intelligence%20sources%20told%20NDTV%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%20The%20report%2C%20sent%20on%20Thursday%2C%20mentioned%20that%20%26quot%3B900%20Kuki%20militants%2C%20newly%20trained%20in%20use%20of%20drone-based%20bombs%2C%20projectles%2C%20missiles%20and%20jungle%20warfare%20have%20entered%20Manipur%20from%20Myanmar%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BKuki%20militants%26quot%3B%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20grouped%20in%20units%20of%2030%20members%20each%20and%20at%20present%20are%20scattered%20in%20the%20periphery%2C%20the%20intelligence%20sources%20told%20NDTV%2C%20adding%20they%20may%20launch%20multiple%20coordinated%20attacks%20on%20Meitei%20villages%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F5n34t4l8_moreh-assam-rifles_625x300_10_February_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20press%20conference%20today%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20they%20believe%20the%20report%20to%20be%20%26quot%3B100%20per%20cent%20correct%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnless%20and%20until%20it%20is%20proved%20wrong%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20it%20is%20100%20per%20cent%20correct.%20Because%20any%20intelligence%20input%20you%20have%20to%20take%20100%20per%20cent%20correct%20and%20prepare%20for%20that.%20If%20it%20doesn't%20come%20true%2C%20then%20there%20are%20two%20things.%20Either%20it%20didn't%20happen%20at%20all%2C%20or%20because%20of%20your%20efforts%20it%20didn't%20happen.%20You%20cannot%20take%20it%20lightly%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEthnic%20armed%20groups%20in%20Myanmar's%20Chin%20State%20and%20other%20states%20have%20been%20fighting%20the%20junta%2C%20and%20have%20taken%20large%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20which%20the%20junta%20earlier%20controlled.%20Some%20of%20the%20fighting%20has%20taken%20place%20close%20to%20the%20border%20with%20India%2C%20with%20instances%20of%20some%20junta%20troops%20fleeing%20into%20India%20after%20Chin%20State%20rebels%20overran%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frow-over-assam-rifles-ex-dg-lt-general-pc-nair-meitei-police-kuki-police-comment-manipur-police-say-myopic-mindset-6536232%5C%22%3ERow%20Over%20Assam%20Rifles%20Ex%20Chief's%20%26quot%3BMeitei%20Police%2C%20Kuki%20Police%26quot%3B%20Comment%3B%20Cops%20Say%20%26quot%3BMyopic%20Mindset%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20government%20has%20long%20maintained%20that%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20the%20state%20was%20a%20direct%20result%20of%20a%20huge%20spike%20in%20the%20population%20of%20illegal%20immigrants%20-%20among%20other%20factors%20-%20in%20southern%20Manipur%2C%20which%20shares%20a%20border%20with%20Chin%20State%20and%20the%20Sagaing%20Region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20on%20a%20question%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-manipur-standoff-between-armoured-vehicle-and-suspected-insurgents-5033646%5C%22%3Eattacks%20on%20police%20commandos%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Manipur's%20border%20trading%20town%20Moreh%2C%20the%20Security%20Adviser%20had%20denied%20the%20involvement%20of%20Myanmar-based%20militants.%20He%20had%2C%20however%2C%20admitted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeitei-alliance-condemns-killing-of-crpf-soldier-by-suspected-kuki-insurgents-in-manipur-jiribam-6112003%5C%22%3Ethere%20was%20a%20possibility%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Myanmar%20militants%20might%20have%20come%2C%20though%20there%20was%20no%20evidence%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fevuvh79o_moreh-assam-rifles_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20villages%20of%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20in%20the%20hills%20surrounding%20the%20Meitei-dominated%20valley.%20The%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meitei%20community%20and%20the%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20tribes%20known%20as%20Kukis%20-%20a%20term%20given%20by%20the%20British%20in%20colonial%20times%20-%20who%20are%20dominant%20in%20some%20hill%20areas%20of%20Manipur%2C%20has%20killed%20over%20220%20people%20and%20internally%20displaced%20nearly%2050%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20category%20Meiteis%20want%20to%20be%20included%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20category%2C%20while%20the%20Kukis%20who%20share%20ethnic%20ties%20with%20people%20in%20neighbouring%20Myanmar's%20Chin%20State%20and%20Mizoram%20want%20a%20separate%20administration%20carved%20out%20of%20Manipur%2C%20citing%20discrimination%20and%20unequal%20share%20of%20resources%20and%20power%20with%20the%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Value%20Of%20Agreements%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20involvement%20of%20overground%20insurgents%20from%20both%20communities%20in%20the%20Manipur%20clashes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fseems-3-kuki-insurgents-from-churachandpur-traversed-long-distance-manipur-police-on-what-happened-in-jiribam-6520704%5C%22%3Ewas%20confirmed%20recently%20by%20the%20police%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20a%20gunfight%20in%20Jiribam%20district%2C%20neighbouring%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20Kuki%20insurgents%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20gunfight%20were%20members%20of%20the%20Kuki%20Liberation%20Army%20(KLA)%2C%20whose%20two%20factions%20are%20part%20of%20the%