s%20use%20the%20act%20to%20fight%20corruption.%20They%20also%20established%20the%20Manjunath%20Shanmugam%20Integrity%20Award%20to%20honour%20individuals%20who%20fought%20against%20systemic%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20fight%20for%20justice%20continued%20until%202015%2C%20as%20the%20convicts%20appealed%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20in%202009%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202015.%20While%20the%20High%20Court%20upheld%20the%20convictions%2C%20it%20commuted%20Mittal%E2%80%99s%20death%20sentence%20to%20life%20imprisonment.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20upheld%20the%20convictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Believe%20that%20the%20system%20works%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20immersing%20yourself%20in%20a%20case%20like%20this%20for%20so%20long%2C%20life%20changes.%20One%E2%80%99s%20perspective%20towards%20life%20evolves%2C%20and%20for%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%2C%20it%20was%20no%20different.%20While%20they%20had%20always%20been%20straightforward%20people%2C%20this%20experience%20made%20them%20even%20more%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-1726828969.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20tips%20to%20be%20a%20good%20citizen%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-1726828969.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-1726828969-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-1726828969-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-1726828969-768x402.jpg%2076