t%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHunting%20in%20pair%20is%20an%20often-used%20maxim%20about%20fast%20bowlers%2C%20but%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20have%20given%20a%20new%20spin%20to%20it%2C%20consistently%20troubling%20the%20opposition%20in%20more%20ways%20than%20one.%20The%20latest%20mission%20by%20the%20Tango%20and%20Cash%20of%20modern%20Indian%20cricket%20was%20against%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20ongoing%20first%20Test%20here%20when%20they%20added%20199%20runs%20for%20the%20seventh%20wicket%20to%20lead%20India%20to%20376%20all%20out%20from%20a%20wispy%20144%20for%20six.%20It%20was%20a%20new%20high%20even%20for%20the%20Ashwin-Jadeja%20combine%2C%20who%20have%20registered%20three%2050-plus%20stands%20together%20to%20steady%20the%20Indian%20ship%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20did%20not%20hide%20his%20admiration%20for%20Jadeja.%20%26quot%3BI%20always%20envy%20him.%20So%20gifted%2C%20so%20talented.%20He's%20found%20ways%20to%20maximise%20his%20potential.%20I%20wish%20I%20could%20be%20him%2C%20but%20I'm%20glad%20I%20am%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20told%20reporters%20during%20the%20post-day%20press%20meet%20in%20Chennai%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chennai%20man%20admitted%20that%20having%20Jadeja%20at%20the%20other%20end%20helped%20him%20constructing%20his%20sixth%20Test%20hundred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20an%20exceptionally%20good%20cricketer.%20I'm%20happy%20for%20him.%20Likewise%2C%20in%20so%20many%20ways%2C%20I%20think%20watching%20him%20bat%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20has%20also%20given%20me%20insight%20on%20how%20better%20I%20can%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20bowling%2C%20Ashwin%20pursues%20a%20vastly%20different%20philosophy%2C%20flummoxing%20batters%20with%20an%20endless%20bag%20of%20tricks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJadeja%20is%20more%20real%20world%2C%20keeping%20it%20tight%20and%20using%20subtle%20changes%20in%20line%20and%20length%20to%20net%2