eps%20that%20need%20to%20be%20taken%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20lack%20of%20concrete%20data%2C%20Dr%20Dar%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20major%20concern%20regarding%20the%20groundwater%20and%20its%20relationship%20with%20different%20environmental%20components%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20the%20data%20and%20understanding%20of%20its%20hydrodynamic%20processes.%20Understanding%20the%20systems%2C%20particularly%20the%20underground%20aquifers%2C%20is%20important.%20There%20is%20a%20crucial%20need%20to%20acquire%20data%20and%20gather%20accurate%20and%20reliable%20information%20on%20groundwater%20quantity%2C%20quality%2C%20and%20flow%20dynamics.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CModern%20tools%20and%20techniques%20like%20remote%20sensing%2C%20geophysics%2C%20tracers%2C%20etc%20are%20widely%20used%20to%20address%20groundwater%20problems.%20For%20this%20funding%20of%20research%20and%20development%20(R%26amp%3BD)%20projects%20is%20necessary.%20The%20effects%20of%20anthropogenic%20activities%2C%20such%20as%20population%20growth%2C%20urbanisation%2C%20and%20land%20use%20changes%20on%20groundwater%20resources%20need%20to%20be%20quantified.%20Integrating%20advanced%20modelling%20techniques%20can%20help%20in%20this%20direction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-2-1-1726237354.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Overview%20of%20Leh%20town%3A%20The%20effects%20of%20growing%20urbanisation%20on%20the%20groundwater%20need%20to%20be%20further%20studied.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-2-1-1726237354.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-2-1-1726237354-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebette